Ashram Creative Lightweight jQuery Fader

Installation:

1.	Upload "ac-fader.css" and "ac-fader.js" to the directory where your page is located.
2.	Make sure that your page is loading the jQuery library.
2.	Load them on the page by inserting:
	<link href="ac-fader.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet"/>
	<script type="text/javascript" language="javascript" src="ac-fader.js"></script>
3.	Add the fader to your page by adding the following HTML into your page:
	<div id="#ac-fader"></div>
4.	Put any images or slides inside the <div#ac-fader>.